---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Tooltails.com" description="Your privacy is our top priority. All age and date calculations happen locally in your browser. Read our full privacy policy.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-ink mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-neutral">
      <p class="text-lg text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        At Tooltails.com, your privacy is our top priority. This policy outlines how we handle your data.
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink mt-12 mb-4">No Data Collection</h2>
      <p class="text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        All calculations performed on Tooltails.com happen locally in your web browser. We do not store, collect, or transmit any personal data, including your date of birth, to our servers.
      </p>
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink mt-12 mb-4">Analytics and Tracking Technologies</h2>
      <p class="text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We use basic analytics tools to understand website traffic and improve user experience. These tools may use cookies, but they are configured to respect your privacy and do not collect personally identifiable information.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink mt-12 mb-4">Google AdSense and Advertising Cookies</h2>
      <p class="text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We use Google AdSense to display advertisements. Third-party vendors, including Google, use cookies to serve ads based on your prior visits to this website or other websites on the internet.
      </p>
      <p class="text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads to you based on your visit to our site and/or other sites across the internet. This allows us to keep our calculators 100% free to use.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink mt-12 mb-4">Personalized Advertising & Opt-Out</h2>
      <p class="text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        You have control over how your data is used for personalized advertising. You can opt out of personalized advertising by visiting Google's <a href="https://myadcenter.google.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-link hover:text-link-hover">Ads Settings</a>. Alternatively, you can opt out of a third-party vendor's use of cookies for personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://youradchoices.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-link hover:text-link-hover">www.aboutads.info</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "WebPage",
    "name": "Privacy Policy - Tooltails.com",
    "description": "Your privacy is our top priority. All age and date calculations happen locally in your browser.",
    "url": Astro.url.origin + "/privacy",
    "mainEntityOfPage": {
      "@type": "WebPage",
      "@id": Astro.url.origin + "/privacy"
    }
  })} />
</Layout>
